<node id="Blount Island">
  <data key="d0">Blount Island</data>
  <data key="d1">location</data>
  <data key="d2">Blount Island is the site associated with shoreline cleanup services under ELIN X718.&lt;SEP&gt;Blount Island is referenced in site visit itineraries, base access forms, and facility inventories under MCSF-BI.&lt;SEP&gt;Blount Island is referenced in the base access form for site visit participation.&lt;SEP&gt;Blount Island is the site for the shoreline cleanup plan and map under grounds maintenance.&lt;SEP&gt;Blount Island is the site of the Marine Corps Support Facility in Jacksonville, Florida, included as a performance location under the solicitation.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-3b65cbb31e854658ff984a34247acde1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-729293c3f8703afb2cb5e31cb6ff90dd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9e005e41da996ebb18d009a4f87b0e3c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6266f048b10bdb8222f03b8f5e597d7e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-516b1e6efecfd543f141d1e1135ec455</data>
