<node id="NAVSTA Mayport">
  <data key="d0">NAVSTA Mayport</data>
  <data key="d1">location</data>
  <data key="d2">A naval station that distributes its own electricity and produces and distributes its own water, requiring adequate utility services.&lt;SEP&gt;NAVSTA Mayport is the naval station that distributes its own electricity and produces and distributes its own water.&lt;SEP&gt;NAVSTA Mayport is referenced in facility inventories, site maps, and historical work orders.&lt;SEP&gt;NAVSTA Mayport is a naval station facility associated with weight handling equipment, cross connection control programs, points of demarcation, utility maps, and storm water pollution prevention plans.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-b1019473eb9ce96e37dbd7a39cfdf02d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ac133babc8ecde7c6f7014a40f53ce13&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-516b1e6efecfd543f141d1e1135ec455&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9e005e41da996ebb18d009a4f87b0e3c</data>
