  <data key="d5">1759790152</data>
</node>
<node id="Marine Corps Support Facility Blount Island">
  <data key="d0">Marine Corps Support Facility Blount Island</data>
  <data key="d1">location</data>
  <data key="d2">Marine Corps Support Facility Blount Island is located in Jacksonville, Florida, and supports outlying areas for Base Operations Support Services.&lt;SEP&gt;Marine Corps Support Facility Blount Island is a support facility in Jacksonville, Florida, primarily receiving custodial, pest control, integrated solid waste management, and grounds maintenance services.&lt;SEP&gt;This facility, abbreviated as MCSF-BI, is associated with site visits, facility investments, and specific system inventories like auxiliary generators and cathodic protection.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-3e097b0647fa14f34c4ff76380ed4beb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f8cbd3bc2ef4445a2ce77064100a7a3e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-516b1e6efecfd543f141d1e1135ec455</data>
