  <data key="d1">statement_of_work</data>
  <data key="d2">The document outlining all requirements, including maintenance of NAVFAC Maximo data throughout.&lt;SEP&gt;Performance Work Statement (PWS) outlines the scope, performance objectives, and standards for services across annexes and sub-annexes.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-b1019473eb9ce96e37dbd7a39cfdf02d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ac133babc8ecde7c6f7014a40f53ce13</data>
