  <data key="d1">evaluation_factor</data>
  <data key="d2">An evaluation factor assessing the offeror's technical approach, including staffing, methodology, and understanding of requirements.&lt;SEP&gt;Factor 3 evaluates Technical Approach, including staffing levels, methodology for annexes and sub-annexes, and understanding of systems, limits of liability, and supply chain management.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-b1019473eb9ce96e37dbd7a39cfdf02d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ac133babc8ecde7c6f7014a40f53ce13</data>
