  <data key="d1">document</data>
  <data key="d2">Basis of Estimate (BOE) provides rationale for labor classification, annual direct and indirect labor hours, data sources, and methodology for each specification item.&lt;SEP&gt;A reasonable estimate supporting staffing levels for each annex, sub-annex, and spec item in Factor 3 evaluation.</data>
