<node id="Liquidated Damages">
  <data key="d0">Liquidated Damages</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Liquidated damages compensate the Government for administrative costs and expenses from unsatisfactory or non-performed work, assessed at 10 percent of the value of defects.&lt;SEP&gt;Liquidated damages compensate the Government for administrative costs and expenses from nonperformed or unsatisfactory performance, calculated per Section H, and assessed at a rate of 10 percent of all observed defects per day of delay.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-96e30762ee04dbe2af303802d3d2a936&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3b65cbb31e854658ff984a34247acde1</data>
