  <data key="d0">52.215-21 Requirements For Certified Cost Or Pricing Data And Data Other Than Certified Cost Or Pricing Data-Modifications Alternate I</data>
  <data key="d1">clause</data>
  <data key="d2">52.215-21 Requirements For Certified Cost Or Pricing Data And Data Other Than Certified Cost Or Pricing Data-Modifications Alternate I requires submission of certified cost or pricing data in a specified format for modifications.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-96e30762ee04dbe2af303802d3d2a936</data>
  <data key="d4">_N6945025R0003.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1759790157</data>
</node>
<node id="52.215-21 Requirements For Certified Cost Or Pricing Data And Data Other Than Certified Cost Or Pricing Data-Modifications Alternate III">
  <data key="d0">52.215-21 Requirements For Certified Cost Or Pricing Data And Data Other Than Certified Cost Or Pricing Data-Modifications Alternate III</data>
  <data key="d1">clause</data>
  <data key="d2">52.215-21 Requirements For Certified Cost Or Pricing Data And Data Other Than Certified Cost Or Pricing Data-Modifications Alternate III requires submission of the cost portion of proposals via electronic media such as CD.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-96e30762ee04dbe2af303802d3d2a936</data>
  <data key="d4">_N6945025R0003.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1759790157</data>
</node>
<node id="52.216-18 Ordering">
  <data key="d0">52.216-18 Ordering</data>
  <data key="d1">clause</data>
  <data key="d2">52.216-18 Ordering governs the issuance of delivery or task orders under the contract, including methods of issuance and precedence over conflicting orders.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-96e30762ee04dbe2af303802d3d2a936</data>
  <data key="d4">_N6945025R0003.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1759790157</data>
</node>
<node id="52.216-19 Order Limitations">
  <data key="d0">52.216-19 Order Limitations</data>
  <data key="d1">clause</data>
  <data key="d2">52.216-19 Order Limitations sets minimum and maximum order amounts, obligations for honoring orders, and procedures for exceeding limitations in requirements contracts.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-96e30762ee04dbe2af303802d3d2a936</data>
  <data key="d4">_N6945025R0003.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1759790157</data>
</node>
<node id="52.216-22 Indefinite Quantity">
  <data key="d0">52.216-22 Indefinite Quantity</data>
  <data key="d1">clause</data>
  <data key="d2">52.216-22 Indefinite Quantity establishes the contract as indefinite-quantity, with estimated quantities, minimum and maximum order requirements, and completion obligations beyond the contract period.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-96e30762ee04dbe2af303802d3d2a936</data>
  <data key="d4">_N6945025R0003.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1759790157</data>
</node>
<node id="52.217-8 Option To Extend Services">
  <data key="d0">52.217-8 Option To Extend Services</data>
  <data key="d1">clause</data>
  <data key="d2">52.217-8 Option To Extend Services allows the Government to require continued performance for up to 6 months at specified rates, exercisable by written notice.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-96e30762ee04dbe2af303802d3d2a936</data>
  <data key="d4">_N6945025R0003.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1759790157</data>
</node>
<node id="52.217-9 Option To Extend The Term Of The Contract">
  <data key="d0">52.217-9 Option To Extend The Term Of The Contract</data>
  <data key="d1">clause</data>
  <data key="d2">52.217-9 Option To Extend The Term Of The Contract permits extension of the contract term up to 96 months total, with preliminary notice requirements.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-96e30762ee04dbe2af303802d3d2a936</data>
  <data key="d4">_N6945025R0003.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1759790157</data>
</node>
<node id="52.219-4 Notice Of Price Evaluation Preference For HUBZone Small Business Concerns">
  <data key="d0">52.219-4 Notice Of Price Evaluation Preference For HUBZone Small Business Concerns</data>
  <data key="d1">clause</data>
  <data key="d2">52.219-4 Notice Of Price Evaluation Preference For HUBZone Small Business Concerns provides a 10 percent evaluation preference for offers from HUBZone small business concerns that have not waived it.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-96e30762ee04dbe2af303802d3d2a936</data>
  <data key="d4">_N6945025R0003.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1759790157</data>
</node>
