</node>
<node id="Dod AAC N68732">
  <data key="d0">Dod AAC N68732</data>
  <data key="d1">other</data>
  <data key="d2">DoDAAC N68732 is the Department of Defense Activity Address Code used for Pay Official in the Wide Area WorkFlow routing data table.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5874f638e9cb9ecd09e53d314b07e103</data>
  <data key="d4">_N6945025R0003.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1759790158</data>
</node>
<node id="Dod AAC N69450">
  <data key="d0">Dod AAC N69450</data>
  <data key="d1">other</data>
  <data key="d2">DoDAAC N69450 is the Department of Defense Activity Address Code used for Issue By and Admin in the Wide Area WorkFlow routing data table.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5874f638e9cb9ecd09e53d314b07e103</data>
  <data key="d4">_N6945025R0003.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1759790158</data>
</node>
<node id="Cpars">
  <data key="d0">Cpars</data>
  <data key="d1">technology</data>
  <data key="d2">CPARS is the contractor performance evaluation report entry system located at http://www.cpars.gov/ used for evaluating contractor performance.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5874f638e9cb9ecd09e53d314b07e103</data>
  <data key="d4">_N6945025R0003.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1759790158</data>
</node>
<node id="Governmentwide Commercial Purchase Card">
  <data key="d0">Governmentwide Commercial Purchase Card</data>
  <data key="d1">other</data>
  <data key="d2">The Governmentwide Commercial Purchase Card program allows authorized Government personnel to order indefinite quantity pre-priced line item services directly through FedMall at offered prices without markup.&lt;SEP&gt;Governmentwide Commercial Purchase Card (GCPC) is the program enabling authorized Government personnel to order IQ pre-priced line item services directly through FedMall.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-3b65cbb31e854658ff984a34247acde1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5874f638e9cb9ecd09e53d314b07e103</data>
  <data key="d4">_N6945025R0003.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1759790158</data>
</node>
<node id="Pgp Personal">
  <data key="d0">Pgp Personal</data>
  <data key="d1">technology</data>
  <data key="d2">PGP Personal is software that contractors must purchase, install, and utilize, or a comparable solution, to decrypt 128-bit encrypted order notification emails from FedMall.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5874f638e9cb9ecd09e53d314b07e103</data>
  <data key="d4">_N6945025R0003.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1759790158</data>
</node>
<node id="External Certification Authority Program">
  <data key="d0">External Certification Authority Program</data>
  <data key="d1">other</data>
  <data key="d2">External Certification Authority (ECA) program is the DoD initiative providing approved certificates to contractors for secure communication with the DoD and authentication to DoD Information Systems.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5874f638e9cb9ecd09e53d314b07e103</data>
  <data key="d4">_N6945025R0003.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1759790158</data>
</node>
<node id="Iq Pre-Priced Line Item Services">
  <data key="d0">Iq Pre-Priced Line Item Services</data>
  <data key="d1">deliverable</data>
  <data key="d2">IQ pre-priced line item services are offered to Government personnel via FedMall orders under the GCPC program without additional markup or handling fees.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5874f638e9cb9ecd09e53d314b07e103</data>
  <data key="d4">_N6945025R0003.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1759790158</data>
</node>
<node id="Solicitation N69450-25-R-0003">
  <data key="d0">Solicitation N69450-25-R-0003</data>
  <data key="d1">document</data>
  <data key="d2">Solicitation N69450-25-R-0003 is a government procurement document that includes attachments on facility inventories and Section K on representations and certifications.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9e005e41da996ebb18d009a4f87b0e3c</data>
  <data key="d4">_N6945025R0003.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1759790158</data>
</node>
<node id="MCSF-BI">
  <data key="d0">MCSF-BI</data>
  <data key="d1">location</data>
  <data key="d2">MCSF-BI is a site with specific sub-annexes for facility management, investment, custodial, pest control, waste management, and grounds maintenance.&lt;SEP&gt;MCSF-BI is a facility linked to multiple inventories including auxiliary generators, cathodic protection systems, compressed air systems, irrigation equipment, lighting systems, lift stations, custodial services, pest control, solid waste management, grounds maintenance, and environmental plans.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9e005e41da996ebb18d009a4f87b0e3c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ac133babc8ecde7c6f7014a40f53ce13</data>
  <data key="d4">_N6945025R0003.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1759790158</data>
</node>
<node id="Section K">
  <data key="d0">Section K</data>
  <data key="d1">section</data>
  <data key="d2">Section K addresses Representations, Certifications, and Other Statements, incorporating FAR and DFARS clauses by reference and full text.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9e005e41da996ebb18d009a4f87b0e3c</data>
  <data key="d4">_N6945025R0003.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1759790158</data>
</node>
<node id="52.204-8 Annual Representations and Certifications">
  <data key="d0">52.204-8 Annual Representations and Certifications</data>
  <data key="d1">clause</data>
  <data key="d2">52.204-8 Annual Representations and Certifications is a FAR clause included in full text, specifying NAICS code, size standards, and applicable representations for offerors.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9e005e41da996ebb18d009a4f87b0e3c</data>
  <data key="d4">_N6945025R0003.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1759790158</data>
</node>
<node id="NAICS 561210">
  <data key="d0">NAICS 561210</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">NAICS 561210 classifies facilities support services, applicable to this solicitation for base operations support.&lt;SEP&gt;NAICS 561210 is the North American Industry Classification System code assigned to this acquisition for Facilities Support Services, with a small business size standard of $47,000,000.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9e005e41da996ebb18d009a4f87b0e3c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f8cbd3bc2ef4445a2ce77064100a7a3e</data>
  <data key="d4">_N6945025R0003.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1759790158</data>
</node>
<node id="Facilities Support Services">
  <data key="d0">Facilities Support Services</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Facilities Support Services is the category of services for the acquisition under NAICS 561210, involving facility maintenance and operations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9e005e41da996ebb18d009a4f87b0e3c</data>
  <data key="d4">_N6945025R0003.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1759790158</data>
</node>
