<node id="Department of Defense">
  <data key="d0">Department of Defense</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">The Department of Defense operates FedMall and establishes programs like the External Certification Authority for secure contractor communications.&lt;SEP&gt;Department of Defense is the federal agency context for DFARS clauses related to compensation of former officials and safeguarding covered defense information.</data>
