  <data key="d0">Jacksonville, FL</data>
  <data key="d1">location</data>
  <data key="d2">Jacksonville, FL is the location of NAVFAC SOUTHEAST ACQUISITION CORE at PO Box 30 NAS Jacksonville.&lt;SEP&gt;Jacksonville, FL is the location for proposal delivery and site visits at NAS Jacksonville.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9775b66c35e6cfe40c05dbf72803d6cd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4bcb91b404a9ca74c18944c1ba7f80a2</data>
