</node>
<node id="Firm-Fixed Price">
  <data key="d0">Firm-Fixed Price</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Firm-Fixed Price is the type of contract contemplated by the Government for award resulting from the solicitation.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9775b66c35e6cfe40c05dbf72803d6cd</data>
  <data key="d4">_N6945025R0003.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1759790160</data>
</node>
<node id="Base Operations Support (BOS)">
  <data key="d0">Base Operations Support (BOS)</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Base Operations Support (BOS) services encompass specific technical annexes for relevant projects in corporate experience evaluation.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9775b66c35e6cfe40c05dbf72803d6cd</data>
  <data key="d4">_N6945025R0003.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1759790160</data>
</node>
<node id="Port Operations">
  <data key="d0">Port Operations</data>
  <data key="d1">requirement</data>
  <data key="d2">Port Operations is a required base operations support service including labor, supervision, and equipment at naval facilities.&lt;SEP&gt;Port Operations (0600000) is an annex similar to RFP requirements that relevant projects must include for evaluation.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-f8cbd3bc2ef4445a2ce77064100a7a3e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9775b66c35e6cfe40c05dbf72803d6cd</data>
  <data key="d4">_N6945025R0003.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1759790160</data>
</node>
<node id="Facility Investment">
  <data key="d0">Facility Investment</data>
  <data key="d1">requirement</data>
  <data key="d2">Facility Investment (1502000) includes service orders, HVAC systems maintenance and repairs, fire protection systems maintenance and repairs, and other items for relevant projects.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9775b66c35e6cfe40c05dbf72803d6cd</data>
  <data key="d4">_N6945025R0003.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1759790160</data>
</node>
<node id="Electrical">
  <data key="d0">Electrical</data>
  <data key="d1">requirement</data>
  <data key="d2">Electrical (1602000) covers transmission and distribution operations, maintenance, and repairs similar to RFP requirements for relevant projects.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9775b66c35e6cfe40c05dbf72803d6cd</data>
  <data key="d4">_N6945025R0003.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1759790160</data>
</node>
<node id="Water">
  <data key="d0">Water</data>
  <data key="d1">requirement</data>
  <data key="d2">Water (1606000) is an annex that relevant projects must encompass as part of BOS services evaluation.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9775b66c35e6cfe40c05dbf72803d6cd</data>
  <data key="d4">_N6945025R0003.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1759790160</data>
</node>
<node id="Relevant Project">
  <data key="d0">Relevant Project</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Relevant Project is defined as projects demonstrating capability in services similar in size, scope, and complexity to the RFP, with a contract value of $15,000,000 per year or greater, either ongoing with 12 months completed or completed within the last five years.&lt;SEP&gt;Relevant Project is defined as contracts valued at $15,000,000 per year or greater, ongoing with at least 12 months performance or completed within the last five years, demonstrating capability for similar services.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9775b66c35e6cfe40c05dbf72803d6cd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ac133babc8ecde7c6f7014a40f53ce13</data>
  <data key="d4">_N6945025R0003.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1759790160</data>
</node>
<node id="Canadian Commercial Corporation">
  <data key="d0">Canadian Commercial Corporation</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Canadian Commercial Corporation is exempt from certified cost or pricing data requirements and provides specific data for fair pricing determination.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9775b66c35e6cfe40c05dbf72803d6cd</data>
  <data key="d4">_N6945025R0003.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1759790160</data>
</node>
<node id="Public Works and Government Services Canada">
  <data key="d0">Public Works and Government Services Canada</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Public Works and Government Services Canada provides analysis to determine fair and reasonable pricing for the Canadian Commercial Corporation.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9775b66c35e6cfe40c05dbf72803d6cd</data>
  <data key="d4">_N6945025R0003.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1759790160</data>
</node>
<node id="Federal Acquisition Regulation (FAR)">
  <data key="d0">Federal Acquisition Regulation (FAR)</data>
  <data key="d1">document</data>
  <data key="d2">Federal Acquisition Regulation (FAR) is the primary regulation for federal acquisitions, referenced in multiple clauses and provisions.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9775b66c35e6cfe40c05dbf72803d6cd</data>
  <data key="d4">_N6945025R0003.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1759790160</data>
</node>
