  <data key="d0">Facility Management (1501000)</data>
  <data key="d1">annex</data>
  <data key="d2">Facility Management (1501000) includes sub-annexes for NAVSTA and MCSF-BI, requiring methodology for performance objectives under Factor 3.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ac133babc8ecde7c6f7014a40f53ce13</data>
  <data key="d4">_N6945025R0003.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1759790164</data>
</node>
<node id="Custodial (1503010)">
  <data key="d0">Custodial (1503010)</data>
  <data key="d1">annex</data>
  <data key="d2">Custodial (1503010) applies to MCSF-BI and requires an approach to service orders and recurring services under Factor 3.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ac133babc8ecde7c6f7014a40f53ce13</data>
  <data key="d4">_N6945025R0003.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1759790164</data>
</node>
<node id="Pest Control (1503020)">
  <data key="d0">Pest Control (1503020)</data>
  <data key="d1">annex</data>
  <data key="d2">Pest Control (1503020) for MCSF-BI, addressed in technical approach for non-recurring and recurring services.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ac133babc8ecde7c6f7014a40f53ce13</data>
  <data key="d4">_N6945025R0003.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1759790164</data>
</node>
<node id="Integrated Solid Waste Management (1503030)">
  <data key="d0">Integrated Solid Waste Management (1503030)</data>
  <data key="d1">annex</data>
  <data key="d2">Integrated Solid Waste Management (1503030) for MCSF-BI, requiring methodology for waste handling and compliance.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ac133babc8ecde7c6f7014a40f53ce13</data>
  <data key="d4">_N6945025R0003.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1759790164</data>
</node>
<node id="Training Pools (1503040)">
  <data key="d0">Training Pools (1503040)</data>
  <data key="d1">annex</data>
  <data key="d2">Training Pools (1503040) is categorized under other facility support, needing approach to maintenance and systems.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ac133babc8ecde7c6f7014a40f53ce13</data>
  <data key="d4">_N6945025R0003.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1759790164</data>
</node>
<node id="Grounds Maintenance and Landscaping (1503050)">
  <data key="d0">Grounds Maintenance and Landscaping (1503050)</data>
  <data key="d1">annex</data>
  <data key="d2">Grounds Maintenance and Landscaping (1503050) for MCSF-BI, included in Factor 3 technical methodology.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ac133babc8ecde7c6f7014a40f53ce13</data>
  <data key="d4">_N6945025R0003.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1759790164</data>
</node>
<node id="Utilities Management (1601000)">
  <data key="d0">Utilities Management (1601000)</data>
  <data key="d1">annex</data>
  <data key="d2">Utilities Management (1601000) is part of Annex 16, requiring understanding of utility services and systems approach.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ac133babc8ecde7c6f7014a40f53ce13</data>
  <data key="d4">_N6945025R0003.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1759790164</data>
</node>
<node id="General Information (0100000)">
  <data key="d0">General Information (0100000)</data>
  <data key="d1">annex</data>
  <data key="d2">General Information (0100000) is an annex excluded from the minimum technical annex/sub-annex requirement for demonstrating relevant projects.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ac133babc8ecde7c6f7014a40f53ce13</data>
  <data key="d4">_N6945025R0003.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1759790164</data>
</node>
<node id="Management and Administration (0200000)">
  <data key="d0">Management and Administration (0200000)</data>
  <data key="d1">annex</data>
  <data key="d2">Management and Administration (0200000) is an annex not considered toward the minimum one other technical annex requirement for relevant projects.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ac133babc8ecde7c6f7014a40f53ce13</data>
  <data key="d4">_N6945025R0003.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1759790164</data>
</node>
<node id="Workforce Management">
  <data key="d0">Workforce Management</data>
  <data key="d1">submission_instruction</data>
  <data key="d2">Workforce Management is a subfactor under Factor 2 requiring a plan for hiring, retaining, organizing, managing, supervising workforce and key personnel, including organization charts and consistency with staffing levels.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ac133babc8ecde7c6f7014a40f53ce13</data>
  <data key="d4">_N6945025R0003.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1759790164</data>
</node>
<node id="Scheduling">
  <data key="d0">Scheduling</data>
  <data key="d1">submission_instruction</data>
  <data key="d2">Scheduling under Factor 2 requires methodology for developing recurring work schedules, minimizing interference, and adjusting for workload fluctuations and contingencies.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ac133babc8ecde7c6f7014a40f53ce13</data>
  <data key="d4">_N6945025R0003.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1759790165</data>
</node>
<node id="HVAC Systems">
  <data key="d0">HVAC Systems</data>
  <data key="d1">technology</data>
  <data key="d2">HVAC Systems require maintenance and repairs as part of Facility Investment (1502000) minimum requirements for relevant projects.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ac133babc8ecde7c6f7014a40f53ce13</data>
  <data key="d4">_N6945025R0003.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1759790165</data>
</node>
<node id="Fire Protection Systems">
  <data key="d0">Fire Protection Systems</data>
  <data key="d1">technology</data>
  <data key="d2">Fire Protection Systems involve maintenance and repairs included in Facility Investment (1502000) for demonstrating relevancy.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ac133babc8ecde7c6f7014a40f53ce13</data>
  <data key="d4">_N6945025R0003.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1759790165</data>
</node>
<node id="Transmission &amp; Distribution">
  <data key="d0">Transmission &amp; Distribution</data>
  <data key="d1">technology</data>
  <data key="d2">Transmission &amp; Distribution operations, maintenance, and repairs are minimum requirements for Electrical (1602000).</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ac133babc8ecde7c6f7014a40f53ce13</data>
  <data key="d4">_N6945025R0003.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1759790165</data>
</node>
<node id="Raw Water Supply">
  <data key="d0">Raw Water Supply</data>
  <data key="d1">technology</data>
  <data key="d2">Raw Water Supply is part of Water (1606000) operations, including treatment plant and distribution system.</data>
