<node id="Multiple Award Contracts (MACs)">
  <data key="d0">Multiple Award Contracts (MACs)</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Multiple Award Contracts (MACs) are contract types where specific task orders, not the entire contract, are considered for project evaluation.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ac133babc8ecde7c6f7014a40f53ce13</data>
  <data key="d4">_N6945025R0003.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1759790165</data>
