  <data key="d0">Jacksonville, Florida</data>
  <data key="d1">location</data>
  <data key="d2">Jacksonville, Florida is the location hosting Naval Station Mayport and Marine Corps Support Facility Blount Island, where base operations support services are to be performed.</data>
