  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Jacobs Technology Inc. is the previous contractor for contract N69450-18-D-1800, providing base operations support services from Tullahoma, Tennessee, with total performance value of $211,045,432.21 over base and option periods.</data>
